      <title>标签外挂一(修改文章样式结构)</title>
      <link href="/2022/08/26/tagPlugins/"/>
      <url>/2022/08/26/tagPlugins/</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="标签外挂"><a href="#标签外挂" class="headerlink" title="标签外挂"></a>标签外挂</h1><div class="note blue info flat"><p>标签外挂是Hexo独有的功能，并不是标准的Markdown格式。以下的写法，只适用于Butterfly主题，用在其它主题上不会有效果，甚至可能会报错。使用前请留意</p></div><div class="note orange warning flat"><p>​标签外挂虽然能为主题带来一些额外的功能和UI方面的强化，但是，标签外挂也有明显的限制，使用时请留意。</p></div><h2 id="注释-Note"><a href="#注释-Note" class="headerlink" title="注释(Note)"></a>注释(Note)</h2><ol><li><p>第一种是Hexo自带的Note通用设置</p><figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">note:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Note tag style values:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - simple    bs-callout old alert style. Default.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - modern    bs-callout new (v2-v3) alert style.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - flat      flat callout style with background, like on Mozilla or StackOverflow.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment">#  - disabled  disable all CSS styles import of note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">style:</span> <span class="string">simple</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">icons:</span> <span class="literal">false</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">border_radius:</span> <span class="number">3</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset lighter of background in % for modern and flat styles (modern: -12 | 12; flat: -18 | 6).</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="comment"># Offset also applied to label tag variables. This option can work with disabled note tag.</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">light_bg_offset:</span> <span class="number">0</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure></li><li><p>自定义Note</p><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note [color] [no-icon] [style] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">Any content (想要输出的内容)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">或</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note [color] [icon] [style] %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">Any content (想要输出的内容)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">属性</th><th align="center">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">color</td><td align="center">配色（default &#x2F; primary &#x2F; success &#x2F; info &#x2F; warning &#x2F; danger&#x2F; blue &#x2F; pink &#x2F; red &#x2F; purple &#x2F; orange &#x2F; green）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">no-icon</td><td align="center">不显示icon</td></tr><tr><td align="center">icon</td><td align="center">显示icon且可自定义icon（仅支持<a href="http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">fontawesome</a> 图标, 也可以配置 no-icon，默认有default,primary,success,info,warning,danger）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">style</td><td align="center">覆盖配置中的样式（simple&#x2F;modern&#x2F;flat&#x2F;disabled）</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note blue info flat"><p>案列如下：   </p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% note info simple %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info modern %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info flat %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info disabled %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note info no-icon %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">info 提示块标籤</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">或</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; simple %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; modern %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; flat %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue &#x27;fas fa-bullhorn&#x27; disabled %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% note blue no-icon %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">2021年快到了....</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endnote %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note info simple"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info modern"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info flat"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info disabled"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note info no-icon flat"><p>info 提示块标籤   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding simple"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding modern"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding flat"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue icon-padding disabled"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div><div class="note blue no-icon flat"><p>2021年快到了….   </p></div></li></ol><h2 id="相册图库-galleryGroup-amp-gallery"><a href="#相册图库-galleryGroup-amp-gallery" class="headerlink" title="相册图库(galleryGroup&amp;gallery)"></a>相册图库(galleryGroup&amp;gallery)</h2><h3 id="图库页面"><a href="#图库页面" class="headerlink" title="图库页面"></a>图库页面</h3><ul><li><p>创建一个新的页面 <mark class="hl-label orange">hexo n page gallery</mark> </p></li><li><p>在 <mark class="hl-label blue">source/gallery/index.md</mark>  文件里面写代码即可</p><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​图库代码如下</p></div><figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gallery-group-main&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">&#123;% galleryGroup name description link img-url %&#125;</span><br><span class="line">&#123;% galleryGroup name description link img-url %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">div</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">属性</th><th align="center">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">name</td><td align="center">图库名字</td></tr><tr><td align="center">description</td><td align="center">图库描述</td></tr><tr><td align="center">link</td><td align="center">连接对应相册地址</td></tr><tr><td align="center">img-url</td><td align="center">图库封面地址</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​Demo</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;gallery-group-main&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% galleryGroup &#x27;漫威&#x27; &#x27;关于漫威的图片&#x27; &#x27;/Gallery/marvel&#x27; https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/8t97aVlp4hgyBGu.jpg %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% galleryGroup &#x27;OH MY GIRL&#x27; &#x27;关于OH MY GIRL的图片&#x27; &#x27;/Gallery/ohmygirl&#x27; https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/hOqbQ3BIwa6KWpo.jpg %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="gallery-group-main">      <figure class="gallery-group">  <img class="gallery-group-img no-lightbox" src='https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/8t97aVlp4hgyBGu.jpg' alt="Group Image Gallery">  <figcaption>  <div class="gallery-group-name">漫威</div>  <p>关于漫威的图片</p>  <a href='/gallery/HongKongDoll'></a>  </figcaption>  </figure>        <figure class="gallery-group">  <img class="gallery-group-img no-lightbox" src='https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/hOqbQ3BIwa6KWpo.jpg' alt="Group Image Gallery">  <figcaption>  <div class="gallery-group-name">OH MY GIRL</div>  <p>关于OH MY GIRL的图片</p>  <a href='/gallery/HongKongDoll'></a>  </figcaption>  </figure>  </div></li></ul><h3 id="子页面"><a href="#子页面" class="headerlink" title="子页面"></a>子页面</h3><ul><li><p>创建一个新的相册子页面 <mark class="hl-label orange">hexo n page xxxx</mark> </p></li><li><p>在 <mark class="hl-label blue">source/gallery/index.md</mark>  文件里面写代码即可</p><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​图片代码如下</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% gallery %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">markdown 图片格式</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endgallery %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​Demo</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% gallery %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">![](https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/Fze9jchtnyJXMHN.jpg)</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endgallery %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="fj-gallery"><p><img src="https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/Fze9jchtnyJXMHN.jpg"></p>          </div><div class="note orange icon-padding flat"><i class="note-icon fas fa-bullhorn"></i><p>​如需要图库相对应子页面，只用把子页面文件夹放在图库文件里面就行了。然后图库代码<mark class="hl-label orange">link属性</mark> 设置为<mark class="hl-label blue">&#x2F;图库文件夹名&#x2F;子页面文件夹名</mark> </p></div></li></ul><h2 id="标签页-tabs"><a href="#标签页-tabs" class="headerlink" title="标签页(tabs)"></a>标签页(tabs)</h2><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​方法如下</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs Unique name, [index] %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;!-- tab [Tab caption] [@icon] --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">Any content (内容信息).</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">属性</th><th align="center">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">Unique name</td><td align="center">标签名称</td></tr><tr><td align="center">index</td><td align="center">当前显示内容的索引号</td></tr><tr><td align="center">Tab caption</td><td align="center">自定义每一个标签的名称</td></tr><tr><td align="center">@icon</td><td align="center">标签图标（支持<a href="http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">fontawesome</a> 图标）</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​Demo</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% tabs test4 1 %&#125;</span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- tab 第一个Tab --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    **tab名字为第一个Tab**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- tab @fab fa-apple-pay --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    **只有图标 没有Tab名字**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code"></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- tab 炸弹@fas fa-bomb --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    **名字+icon**</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &lt;!-- endtab --&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&#123;% endtabs %&#125;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="tabs" id="test4-1"><ul class="nav-tabs"><li class="tab active"><button type="button" data-href="#test4-1-1">第一个Tab</button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#test4-1-2"><i class="fab fa-apple-pay" style="text-align: center;"></i></button></li><li class="tab"><button type="button" data-href="#test4-1-3"><i class="fas fa-bomb"></i>炸弹</button></li></ul><div class="tab-contents"><div class="tab-item-content active" id="test4-1-1"><p><strong>tab名字为第一个Tab</strong> </p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="test4-1-2"><p><strong>只有图标 没有Tab名字</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div><div class="tab-item-content" id="test4-1-3"><p><strong>名字+icon</strong></p><button type="button" class="tab-to-top" aria-label="scroll to top"><i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i></button></div></div></div><h2 id="按钮-button"><a href="#按钮-button" class="headerlink" title="按钮(button)"></a>按钮(button)</h2><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​方法如下</p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">&#123;% btn [url],[text],[icon],[color] [style] [layout] [position] [size] %&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><table><thead><tr><th align="center">属性</th><th align="center">用法</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td align="center">[url]</td><td align="center">跳转链接</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[text]</td><td align="center">按钮文字</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[icon]</td><td align="center">图标（支持<a href="http://www.fontawesome.com.cn/faicons/">fontawesome</a> 图标）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[color]</td><td align="center">按钮背景颜色（default&#x2F;blue&#x2F;pink&#x2F;red&#x2F;purple&#x2F;orange&#x2F;green）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[style]</td><td align="center">按钮样式，默认实心（outline 留空）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[layout]</td><td align="center">按钮布局，默认为line（block 留空）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[position]</td><td align="center">按钮位置，前提是设置了layout为block（left&#x2F;center&#x2F;right）</td></tr><tr><td align="center">[size]</td><td align="center">按钮大小（larger &#x2F;留空）</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="note blue info flat"><p>​Demo  仅展示部分案列，如有需要请访问<a href="https://butterfly.js.org/posts/4aa8abbe/#Button">官网案列</a></p></div><figure class="highlight markdown"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="language-xml"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">div</span> <span class="attr">class</span>=<span class="string">&quot;btn-center&quot;</span>&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline blue larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline pink larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline red larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline purple larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline orange larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">    &#123;% btn &#x27;https://butterfly.js.org/&#x27;,Butterfly,far fa-hand-point-right,outline green larger %&#125;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="code">&lt;/div&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div class="btn-center"><a class="btn-beautify outline larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline blue larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline pink larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline red larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline purple larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline orange larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a><a class="btn-beautify outline green larger" href="https://butterfly.js.org/"   title="Butterfly"><i class="far fa-hand-point-right"></i><span>Butterfly</span></a></div>]]></content>
      
      
      
